item.title: CVE-2022-4373|2024-08-03T01:34:50.188Z -- unknown -- quote-o-matic
item.description: The Quote-O-Matic WordPress plugin through 1.0.5 does not properly sanitize and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by high privilege users such as admin.
